daY","text_ar":"هَدَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He guided himself."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went a right way: went aright."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA","text_ar":"لَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yahotadiY A_ilaY jihapK","text_ar":"يَهْتَدِى اـِلَى جِهَةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cannot go aright: or knows not the way that he would pursue; or knows not in what direction to go:"},{"kind":"text","text":"sometimes said of a drunken man. ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yahotadiY liA^amorihi","text_ar":"لَا يَهْتَدِى لِاَمْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He does not,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cannot, find the way to accomplish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perform, his affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AihotadaY","text_ar":"اِهْتَدَى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He found,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the right way"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"road."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, KL.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAhiyapu lAa yuhotadaY lahaA","text_ar":"دَاهِيَةُ لاَ يُهْتَدَى لَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", by which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAhiyapu Algabari","text_ar":"دَاهِيَةُ الغَبَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is expl. in the S and O, means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yuhotadaY ll~an~ajaA='i","text_ar":"لَا يُهْتَدَى للَّنَّجَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohaA","text_ar":"مِنْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", by which the same phrase is expl. in the JK: or it may be well rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A calamity in relation to which one knows not the right course to pursue."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AihotadaY","text_ar":"اِهْتَدَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He continued to be rightly directed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to follow a right dirertion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sought to be rightly directed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to follow a right direction."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aihad~aY","text_ar":"اِهَدَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aihid~iY","text_ar":"اِهِدِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AihotadaY","text_ar":"اِهْتَدَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiEa*~ara","text_ar":"اِعَذَّرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiEi*~ira","text_ar":"اِعِذِّرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiEota*ara","text_ar":"اِعْتَذَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["MA","KL"]}]}}